#

Sheet Pan Pork Fajitas

40 min
$15.99
350 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 4

Dietary Tags:

High ProteinGluten-Free

Cuisine:

Mexican

Course:

Main

Tags:

EasySheet PanMexican

Description

A flavor-packed, easy-to-make dish featuring tender pork and colorful bell peppers, all roasted to perfection on a single sheet pan!

Ingredients

  • pork tenderloin: 1 pound
  • bell peppers (red, yellow, green): 3, sliced
  • red onion: 1, sliced
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • lime juice: 2 tablespoons
  • tortillas: 8, for serving
  • salt: 1 teaspoon
  • black pepper: 1/2 teaspoon
  • cumin: 1 teaspoon
  • paprika: 1 teaspoon
  • chili powder: 1 teaspoon
